reviews.reviewText: All my life I've had issues with deodorants either leaving white yucky stuff on your clothes or just plain not working and having to reapply it several times a day..My mom is the one that told me about this brand and I decided to try it and I never ever will use any other deodorant again.. when you apply it you do have to let it dry but it doesn't take long this deodorant works fantastic I've never had an odor issue ever again I've never had an issue with it getting on my clothes and staining because it's clear and gel and it's unscented so it doesn't clash with any perfume or powder or lotion scent.I definitely recommend this to people who have odor issue and have to reapply their deodorant often and I've noticed too that I do not sweat under my underarms I sweat everywhere else!! But not under my underarms which is great!! The price is great and the fact that I can order it on Amazon and have it delivered is even better... 👍👍👍

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 8, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Lasts forever for us sweaty people.
reviews.reviewText: Mitchum Men's Deodorant, the Antiperspirant Triple Odor Defense Gel Stick, has been a reliable companion in my daily routine. Here's why I've found it to be a solid choice:Exceptional Protection: Mitchum delivers on its promise of 48-hour protection. It keeps me feeling fresh and odor-free throughout the day, even during strenuous activities. The level of protection is truly impressive.Dermatologist-Approved: As someone with sensitive skin, I appreciate that this deodorant is dermatologist-approved. It doesn't irritate my skin or cause discomfort, which is a significant plus.Efficiency: The gel stick format may not be my personal preference as I find it gets used up faster compared to the roll-on version. However, it still offers good protection. I just wish it lasted longer.Overall Satisfaction: While I prefer the roll-on version for its longevity, I am still quite happy with the performance of this gel stick. It effectively combats odor and keeps me feeling fresh. It's a dependable choice for daily use.In conclusion, Mitchum Men's Triple Odor Defense Deodorant Gel Stick provides reliable and long-lasting protection. While I have a slight preference for the roll-on version due to its efficiency, this gel stick is still a solid performer. If you're seeking dependable odor protection and don't mind replacing it a bit more frequently, Mitchum's gel stick is a worthwhile option to consider.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Best deodorant I've ever used
reviews.reviewText: For me, there are certain brands that are unrivaled. Dawn for dish soap for example. Mitchum is my deodorant for life. This stuff is amazing. It goes on easy and dries very quickly. It wont stain clothing or clash with your cologne. It has a faint clean almost medicinal scent but is essentially unscented. This literally is miss-a-day protection. If you're in a rush and forget to put it on on in the morning, you are covered. Others have claimed that, but this is the first one I've used that can back that claim up.

reviews.reviewTitle: As good as store-bought. Good for travel.
reviews.reviewText: I have used Mitchum for years and it works effectively. I'm a female student in my 20s who mostly works at a desk, exercises a few times a week and walks a lot. I never feel self-conscious about my odour or perspiring too much. It came as it would when I buy it in the supermarket.It is 100ml so can carried in one's carry-on. I went through airport security twice in three different countries with it with no issue.
Have been a fan of mitchm. Great product and avoids any body odour .Shipping is comparatively faster ,even if it is imported from US.
